---
const areas = ['Montgomery County', 'Prince George’s County', 'Howard County', 'Baltimore area'];
---
<section class="section service-section" id="service-area" aria-labelledby="service-area-title">
  <div class="container service-panel">
    <p class="eyebrow">Service Area</p>
    <h2 id="service-area-title">Serving Maryland families.</h2>
    <p class="service-copy">
      Private swim lessons are available across Montgomery County, Prince George’s County, Howard County, and the Baltimore area. Exact locations are confirmed during scheduling based on pool access and availability.
    </p>
    <div class="area-list" aria-label="Service areas">
      {areas.map((area) => <span>{area}</span>)}
    </div>
    <p class="service-note">
      Lessons may take place at client-provided pools, private or residential pools, and community pools when available.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
